* -5 to party member Perception

drawings.text:
* Assumes tundra/snowshoe travel

* Snowshoes = no additional benfit on roads

* Dogsleds/Reindeer 2x speed on roads

* Axebeaks 2x speed in Tundra

* Mountains reduce all speeds by half
